<span id="freeTextContainer13661760272805960348">Love this author. Here&apos;s a quote from Perrotta from a 2017 interview, answering a question about his characters:<br/>&quot;Most of us want to feel like we&apos;re doing the right thing even when we&apos;re doing the wrong thing. That kind of emotional math is really fascinating to me—the rationalizations and justifications we use.&quot;</span>
  <span id="freeText13661760272805960348" style="display:none">Love this author. Here's a quote from Perrotta from a 2017 interview, answering a question about his characters:<br />"Most of us want to feel like we're doing the right thing even when we're doing the wrong thing. That kind of emotional math is really fascinating to me—the rationalizations and justifications we use."</span>
